    "body": "In the code sandbox (need to test on actual app), I was able to make it work by adding an `<InstantSearchSSRProvider  initialResults={{}} />` (`initialResults` required) wrapping the nested `<InstantSearch />`, is that expected?\r\n\r\nI mean, Is it required to have an `InstantSearchSSRProvider` wrapping every `InstantSearch` even though I only care about hydrating the one at the top level?",
